  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "An evening prayer in pure resonance. Triangle tones drift through 64 panes at a barely-perceptible 0.08 Hz with a near-eternal damp and max Q of 160, the sound existing more in the reverb than in the source. Legato voice mode, a 1.2-second inhale, and a release that outlives the note itself.",
  "tags": ["atmosphere", "breath", "vespers", "ambient", "drone", "legato", "reverb-forward", "slow"],
